CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Ucommune International Ltd is an agile office space provider and manager. The company provides specialized, integrated services for managing agile office spaces and solutions in China. It provides open station spaces, private office spaces, and hourly desks. Its operating segment includes Workspace membership; Marketing and branding services and Other services. The company generates maximum revenue from the Workspace membership.
